snippet.title: Out of Space - Teaser (2019)
snippet.description:
New game from the same creators of Knights of Pen & Paper, Chroma Squad and Galaxy of Pen & Paper. A complete new experience about living together in space. Soon, on Steam Early Access.

Steam Link:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/400080/Out_of_Space/
